data.description: This home has 2 Primary Bedrooms with walk-in closets both upstairs. The Seller has updated major components (HVAC) and interior upgrades with professionally installed ceiling fans w/lights, newer tall kitchen cabinets, breakfast nook storage pantry, & custom bar counter top. The 2 car garage has been finished with the insulated garage door, exhaust fan and a 3M water purification system. The interior lot places you far away from the street noise and a short walk from the pool. Be close to shopping centers, freeways, restaurants, parks, & SUMMERLIN!
